    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle is a straightforward opportunity for the right buyer. It offers dependable transportation value for someone seeking an affordable car, a starter vehicle, or a practical project. Presented honestly and backed by a reputable seller, it stands out as a sensible low-cost option with real potential.",
