      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough with loads of personality, this car has the kind of well-traveled character that turns heads for all the right reasons. It\u2019s an affordable way into ownership for someone who appreciates a machine with a story and sees the potential in giving it a fresh chapter. Perfect as a budget-friendly daily, a hands-on project, or a dependable extra set of wheels for the driveway. If you like cars with soul instead of sameness, this one is ready for its next adventure.",
      "price": 6950.0,
