      "description": "If you\u2019re after a budget-friendly car with plenty of potential, this one could be a great fit. It\u2019s not perfect, but it\u2019s an honest vehicle that could suit someone handy, a project buyer, or anyone needing affordable wheels. A straightforward sale from someone who appreciates a good car and wants to see it go to the right home.",
